casebody.data:
STATE TREASURER, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Larry R. BROWN, Defendant-Appellant,
and
Michelle M. Brown, West Michigan Credit Union, and Office of Retirement Services, Defendants. SC: 158842
COA: 343703 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 28, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the November 13, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
